      <title>Error: Comments Not Initialized</title>
      <link href="/2018/06/05/Error-Comments-Not-Initialized/"/>
      <url>/2018/06/05/Error-Comments-Not-Initialized/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>第一次用Hexo创建博客时用的是<a href="https://github.com/codefine/hexo-theme-mellow" target="_blank" rel="noopener">mellow主题</a>，该主题里评论系统设置了两个：</p><ol><li><p>valine</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">valine:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: false</span><br><span class="line">  appid: #appid</span><br><span class="line">  appkey: #appkey</span><br><span class="line">  notify: true  #是否开启邮箱提醒</span><br><span class="line">  verify: true  #是否开启验证码</span><br><span class="line">  placeholder: give me some sugers plz... #留言板中的预留信息</span><br><span class="line">  avatar: &apos;wavatar&apos;  #用户头像</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><ol start="2"><li><p>gitment</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gitment:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  lazy: true </span><br><span class="line">  owner: ##gitHub账号名 </span><br><span class="line">  repo: ##gitHub账号名下创建一个gitment的项目（可以是个空项目） </span><br><span class="line">  oauth: </span><br><span class="line">  client_id: ##创建OAuth Apps后生成的Client ID</span><br><span class="line">  client_secret: ##创建OAuth Apps后生成的Client Secret</span><br><span class="line">  perPage: 10</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p>我用到的则是第二个，在按照该作者的<a href="https://github.com/codefine/hexo-theme-mellow/wiki/4.-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8Egithub%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F-gitment" target="_blank" rel="noopener">详细文档</a>设置后在博客页面上始终提示Error: Comments Not Initialized，点击Login则跳转到博客主页</p><p>后来实在没办法只好问作者本人，解决办法如下：</p><ol><li>通过nginx配置把带www的URL跳转到一级域名 （这是当时我百度的，但是没解决我的问题，可能会解决别的问题，暂时加上）</li><li>在头像–Settings–Developer settings–OAuth Apps中找到配置的Homepage URL 以及Authorization callback URL <figure class="image-box">                <img src="C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Local\Temp\1528187303127.png" alt="1528187254963](C:UsersAdministratorAppDataLocalTemp1528187254963.png)，确保这两个配置跟Github的Repository Settings里的GitHub Pages---Enforce HTTPS 选中（选中则表示以https协议，不选择以http）![1528187303127" title="" class="">                <p>1528187254963](C:UsersAdministratorAppDataLocalTemp1528187254963.png)，确保这两个配置跟Github的Repository Settings里的GitHub Pages---Enforce HTTPS 选中（选中则表示以https协议，不选择以http）![1528187303127</p>            </figure>协议一致</li></ol><p>更改后保存直接刷新页面，然后点击Login，成功绑定，成功初始化，至此问题解决，特写下此文来记录下</p>]]></content>
      
